{"fixed_xml":"<ITEM>
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Falckeisische Bibel</TITLE>
    noch gantz neu in 
    <FORMAT>Schweins-leder</FORMAT>
    gebunden, 
    <PRIZE>12. Gulden</PRIZE>
  </BIBL>
  oder gegen einem neuen 
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Corpore Juris</TITLE>
    , 
    <PLACE>Leipziger Edition</PLACE>
    , zu vertauschen.
  </BIBL>
</ITEM>","number_of_corrections":5,"explanation":"The input was a JSON object containing an 'xml_string'. I extracted the XML content and corrected/restructured it. The original XML was missing a root element, so I added '<ITEM>' as the root. I removed the leading '20. ' which seemed like an external list number rather than part of the book entry structure. I also cleaned up the structure by placing the prize information correctly within the first BIBL block and ensuring proper nesting for the second BIBL block. The symbols '\u221a\u2020' were removed as they appeared extraneous."}
